headline: 3 Major Regional Banks to Watch as Industry Prospects Remain Robust
summary: BNY Mellon, Truist and Northern Trust are well-positioned for growth as the Zacks Major Regional Banks industry benefits from restructuring & acquisitions, digitization, modest loan demand and Fed policy shifts.
